May 13th, 2017 X-Wing Vassal news

The latest 7.0.1 X-Wing module release blog post can be found here: https://teamcovenant.com/?p=68545

The Vassal "off-season" league is in signup phase until June 1st. Read the details here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YGdZsc1Ql65k9-ESFwfMpY-bDJ90tMMy3ZwPhV9nCcY/edit

The Vassal league season 4 has ended on April 17th. Signup for season 5 will start some time near the end of the summer. Go here to read about it: https://www.reddit.com/r/xwingonline/comments/631ir1/league_newsletter_422017/

Reddit X-Wing Tournament 7 is in signup phase until May 15th 2017. Details: https://www.reddit.com/r/XWingTMG/comments/68q895/rxt_season_7_signups_due_51517/ 

Team Covenant Open organized by Theorist is now running with special rules. Specs here: https://teamcovenant.com/star-wars-x-wing/tc-open-sign-up-announcement
Round 2 here: https://teamcovenant.com/star-wars-x-wing/tc-spring-open-standings-and-round-2-pairings
